  <section>
    <div class="title">
      <h3>ENTRY POINTS</h3>
      <p>We defined distinct capabilities for Bankers and Marketers within the IQ Shell so each role could focus on the tasks most relevant to them. Although we designed an information architecture for a dedicated Marketer experience, it wasn’t implemented in this phase due to resource constraints. Instead, both roles enter through the same path—IQ Shell → Engagement Center → Campaign tab—where the experience adapts based on whether the user is a Banker or a Marketer. This helped us preserve role-specific functionality without adding unnecessary complexity.</p>
