      <h3>CAMPAIGN & EVENT FORMS</h3>
      <p>The Campaign Creation Form, designed specifically for iQ marketers, transforms the way campaigns and events are planned and managed. Built around the marketer’s journey, it provides a clear, step-by-step process for essential tasks. From gauging nomination ranges to scheduling key phases like nominations, email dispatch, and campaign duration, the form puts everything marketers need right at their fingertips—making campaign management faster, easier, and more intuitive.</p>
