  <section>
    <div class="title">
      <h3>CAMPAIGN & EVENT NOMINATIONS</h3>
      <p>In addition to campaign creation, we introduced a Nominate to Campaign feature to address a key pain point around lead nomination. Marketers now have four flexible and intuitive ways to nominate leads or contacts:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Individual Search:</strong> Find a lead or contact by name.</li>
        <li><strong>Bulk Upload:</strong> Upload a file containing multiple clients at once.</li>
        <li><strong>Import from Campaign:</strong> Pull members from an existing campaign into a new one, saving time.</li>
        <li><strong>Build Your Audience:</strong> Customize searches to screen and select leads and contacts.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
