  <section>
    <div class="title">
      <h3>EVENT WAITLIST</h3>
      <p>For in-person or event campaigns, we introduced an Approval Queue  (previously known as the waitlist) to bring clarity and structure to the approval process while empowering marketers to manage attendance effectively. In this flow:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Event marketers can nominate members directly into the queue.</li>  
        <li>They can assign specific approvers responsible for reviewing nominations.</li>  
        <li>Approvers review nominations and update member status from Pending Review to Approved as appropriate.</li>  
        <li>Event managers can then move approved members into the main campaign list, considering factors like event capacity, line of business, or other internal criteria.</li>  
      </ul>
    </div>
