  <section>
    <div class="title">
      <h3>DELIVERY & IMPLEMENTATION</h3>
      <p>We iterated on the campaign creation workflow based on user and stakeholder feedback, refining designs to better meet marketer needs. Key enhancements included form filling, editing, deleting, file uploads, and handling errors in multiple member nominations. We consolidated processes from Salesforce, Dash Nominator, and GEM into a single IQ Marketer platform, ensuring a smoother, more intuitive workflow.</p>
      <p>We also conducted user testing with several marketers—feedback was overwhelmingly positive, with users finding the UI intuitive and tasks easier to complete. Areas needing clarification, such as required vs. optional fields, time inputs, and terminology, were addressed and improvements were implemented within our scope.</p>
    </div>
