      <p>This project highlights the value of cross-team collaboration, bringing together design, research, content, and product marketing teams to align the needs of diverse stakeholders—from bankers and sales enablement to marketers and event planners. Together, we merged three CRMs (Customer Relationship Management systems.) into a single IQ platform, developed marketer-focused campaign creation tools, and built a more integrated and effective system. IQ Marketer will transform how marketers manage campaigns, equipping them with the tools needed to drive better business outcomes.</p>
